  "detailed_description": "<strong>Haunted Tower</strong> is a clever tower defense game about Strategy, not Gems. Place towers to prepare your defenses and use abilities to battle waves of ghosts rising from the grave. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242930/extras/f02fe2f10796ed7b6e14642bda95badb.poster.avif?t=1722014131\" width=620 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242930/extras/f02fe2f10796ed7b6e14642bda95badb.webm?t=1722014131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242930/extras/f02fe2f10796ed7b6e14642bda95badb.mp4?t=1722014131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How long can you survive the swarm?</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242930/extras/af1faca6d601aa373a8568d496f99f08.avif?t=1722014131\" width=630 height=70 /></span><br><br>In the haunted town of Drobeta, an evil ghost named <strong>Arbella Stuart</strong> has been terrorizing the residents for centuries. As the town's only hope, you must use your strategic thinking skills to build towers against Arbella and her ghostly army.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242930/extras/bb886c7b485b764d75c949a623b62166.avif?t=1722014131\" width=630 height=70 /></span><br><br>Choose between multiple game modes and experience a different way to play the game.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Campaign</h2> Casual, relaxing, and short levels<br></li><li> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survival</h2> Exciting and prolonged sessions</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242930/extras/e9f8bb4a62ca33e027c27c996bb0280f.avif?t=1722014131\" width=630 height=70 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Three difficulty levels for the Campaign<br></li><li> Score multiplier for Survival<br></li><li> Four tower types with upgrades (three levels)<br></li><li> Two abilities (EMP and Vortex)<br></li><li> Two game speeds<br></li><li> Fast-forward<br></li><li> Timewarp<br></li><li> Call the next wave early<br></li><li> Repair base<br></li><li> Destroyable items<br></li><li> Road obstacles<br></li><li> Pedestals<br></li><li> Multiple spawn locations</li></ul>",
